latestIgtvVideos.title: HOW TO SELECT THE CORRECT FOUNDATION
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
When selecting a foundation:
-Check your undertone ( warm / cool/ Neutral )
- Match the foundation to your neck and chest color 
- Always use a corrector under the foundation for dark spots / pigmentation 
-Use a setting powder with the same undertone

latestIgtvVideos.title: DIY FACE SCRUB FOR DRY ACNE PRONE SKIN
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
You can have natural glowing skin with just products you’ll find in your cupboard. 

While you’re here have you checked out my 90 day to forever youth program? You’ll be equipped with everything you need to have healthy, younger looking skin in a hands-on program from me. 
.
DIY MASK INGREDIENTS:
-Walnuts
-Milk ( you can use almond milk as well)
-Fresh Tumeric peices - to treat acne scars 
-3 drops of vitamin E oil ( this is excellent for acne prone dry skin )
- 1/2 teaspoon honey - if the skin is extremely dry 
.
.
IMP :
-Make sure to steam your face before any face mask.
-Apply it in the upward motion 
- If you have sensitive skin - try a patch on your forearm and then try anything new on the face.
.
.
.
